title: Paedophile films sex with five-year-old son
text:
Paedophile films sex with five-year-old son 
New Kerala Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Pescara, Oct 23 : Police in Italy arrested a woman paedophile and her cousin after seizing photos and videos from the pair that included images of the woman having sex with her five-year-old son.
